ainst him whenever he passes by.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.15846,0.25989,0.17276,0.076854,0.061074,0.067941,0.044507,0.056743,0.03162,0.027704,0.022756,0.019687],"unified_progress":[0.13069,0.17218,0.13512,0.090383,0.080042,0.086045,0.063686,0.081352,0.050388,0.044373,0.036867,0.028871]},{"section":4,"text":"That sounds like paranoia.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.10426,0.1502,0.14134,0.11625,0.092948,0.079484,0.068779,0.065181,0.051996,0.05419,0.039462,0.035909],"unified_progress":[0.11393,0.10531,0.09912,0.10312,0.093698,0.088952,0.082489,0.081439,0.067687,0.071124,0.052237,0.0409]},{"section":5,"text":"Then he thinks his wife has been replaced by a double, which is a classic Capgras delusion.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.096789,0.14622,0.1192,0.099306,0.089608,0.088517,0.076385,0.076427,0.061259,0.056968,0.047185,0.042136],"unified_progress":[0.094115,0.10779,0.10409,0.096429,0.091784,0.093301,0.084184,0.086624,0.073418,0.066961,0.055913,0.045392]},{"section":6,"text":"He's even calling the police, showing he's taking these beliefs seriously.","dimension":10,"group":5,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.11068,0.16918,0.12808,0.091888,0.078144,0.08312,0.067548,0.076261,0.05714,0.052895,0.044598,0.040471],"unified_progress":[0.10799,0.12452,0.10354,0.095186,0.085911,0.087382,0.077056,0.084283,0.069787,0.064421,0.055162,0.044756]},{"section":7,"text":"Hmm, so the key symptoms here are the persistent paranoid beliefs and the delusion about his wife being replaced.","dimension":13,"group":2,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.094199,0.13139,0.11849,0.10227,0.088959,0.081259,0.073725,0.074573,0.062241,0.066732,0.052668,0.053492],"unified_progress":[0.10597,0.090862,0.088414,0.091605,0.089,0.087998,0.084313,0.08603,0.075688,0.077788,0.065217,0.057114]},{"section":8,"text":"Capgras syndrome is when someone believes a loved one has been replaced by an impostor.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.062718,0.10099,0.098583,0.098878,0.099328,0.097284,0.092002,0.086656,0.075276,0.071878,0.060404,0.056001],"unified_progress":[0.064506,0.076864,0.095191,0.093467,0.095102,0.1007,0.094375,0.092867,0.084923,0.07891,0.066581,0.056512]},{"section":9,"text":"That's definitely part of it.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.048327,0.088079,0.10263,0.10534,0.10042,0.092256,0.088968,0.083378,0.078058,0.080588,0.066832,0.065122],"unified_progress":[0.053633,0.072319,0.083344,0.09529,0.096072,0.094754,0.093806,0.092128,0.087975,0.089809,0.076146,0.064724]},{"section":10,"text":"But the paranoia about neighbors planning against him could be part of a broader psychotic disorder.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.052015,0.090646,0.097363,0.099059,0.096451,0.09164,0.089033,0.085803,0.08026,0.080687,0.070087,0.066956],"unified_progress":[0.057849,0.071672,0.081313,0.090165,0.092329,0.093369,0.093931,0.093357,0.090073,0.089622,0.079137,0.067184]},{"section":11,"text":"Now, considering the duration\u201410 years.","dimension":3,"group":8,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.053662,0.090385,0.096896,0.097563,0.0949,0.091078,0.087247,0.085122,0.080775,0.082288,0.071822,0.068263],"unified_progress":[0.07136,0.077931,0.081663,0.088682,0.089832,0.089942,0.090605,0.09091,0.086648,0.088314,0.077902,0.066212]},{"section":12,"text":"That's a long time.","dimension":-1,"group":-1,"is_degenerate":true,"model_progress":[0.32457,0.053564,0.053603,0.062601,0.063177,0.063992,0.061007,0.067401,0.068876,0.064457,0.06724,0.049515],"unified_progress":[0.22396,0.089339,0.063216,0.063751,0.073404,0.072435,0.088479,0.078034,0.075061,0.061035,0.056928,0.054355]},{"section":13,"text":"Schizophrenia typically has a chronic course with psychotic symptoms like delusions and hallucinations.","dimension":8,"group":3,"is_degenerate":false,"model_progress":[0.04